'''策林·托傑'''（{{dz|d=ཚེ་རིང་སྟོབས་རྒྱས།|t=Tshering Tobgay}}，{{bd|1965年|9月19日|catIdx=Tobgay, Tshering}}），一譯'''策林·托布蓋'''<ref>{{cite news |author1=王兴栋 |title=最帅国王的“最幸福”婚礼 |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-05-29/124022550038.shtml |accessdate=2021-09-02 |work=国际周刊 |publisher=新浪网 |date=2011-05-29 |archive-date=2021-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210902150624/https://widget.weibo.com/relationship/bulkfollow.php?refer=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-05-29/124022550038.shtml&uids=1907947932,1934093465,1931971507,1455690987,1753009580&color=cccccc,f5f8fd,000099,666666&showtitle=0&showinfo=1&count=5&sense=1&wide=2&verified=0&ch=sina-news-zw-1-0&dpc=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[不丹|不丹]]政治家，曾於2013年至2018年期間出任[[不丹首相|不丹首相]]。

== 生平 ==
策林·托傑生於1965年9月19日，是家中的長子，有六個弟弟，父親是軍官，母親是修路工人。他在[[印度|印度]][[卡林邦|卡林邦]]{{en-link|葛雷漢博士之家|Dr. Graham's Home}}寄宿學校完成中學課程<ref>{{cite news|author=Sonam Pelden|title=Politician by chance, PM by choice|url=http://www.kuenselonline.com/politician-by-chance-pm-by-choice/#.Uf5oVtJTRYU|accessdate=2013-08-04|newspaper=Kuensel|date=2013-07-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801061651/http://www.kuenselonline.com/politician-by-chance-pm-by-choice/#.Uf5oVtJTRYU|archivedate=2013-08-01}}</ref>，之後在1990年考獲[[美國|美國]][[匹茲堡大學|匹茲堡大學]]機械工程學碩士學位。返回不丹後，他在1991年加入教育科工業及職業教育分科，展開16年的公職生涯，然後於1999年參與成立國家技術訓練局，並擔任主席。托傑在2003年轉任勞工及人力資源部人力署署長，並於翌年考獲美國[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]公共行政碩士學位<ref>{{cite web |title=Keynote Address by His Excellency Lyonchhen Dasho Tshering Tobgay, the Hon’ble Prime Minister of Bhutan |url=http://www.bhutanstudies.org.bt/publicationFiles/ConferenceProceedings/6th%20GNH%20Conferencing/Keynote%20Address.pdf |publisher=Centre for Bhutan Studies and Gross National Happiness |location=Thimphu |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2021-09-02 |archive-date=2019-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802085625/http://www.bhutanstudies.org.bt/publicationFiles/ConferenceProceedings/6th%20GNH%20Conferencing/Keynote%20Address.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2007年，托傑辭去公務員職務，並成為不丹第一個政黨——[[人民民主黨_(不丹)|人民民主黨]]的創黨黨員<ref name="pdp">{{cite web |title=President |url=http://pdp.bt/president |publisher=People's Democratic Party |accessdate=2013-07-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030134149/http://pdp.bt/president |archivedate=2013-10-30 }}</ref>。2008年3月，不丹舉行首屆[[2008年不丹國民議會選舉|國民議會選舉]]，由人民民主黨和[[不丹繁榮進步黨|不丹繁榮進步黨]]的候選人角逐47個議席，結果人民民主黨落敗，黨魁[[桑格·乃杜|桑格·乃杜]]落選<ref name="reuters"/>，但是托傑卻在不丹西部[[哈阿宗|哈阿宗]]一個選區當選，成為人民民主黨兩名議員之一<ref>{{cite web |title=Statistical Information on Elections in Bhutan (2006-2015) |url=https://www.ecb.bt/rnp/election.pdf |publisher=Election Commission of Bhutan |location=Thimphu |accessdate=2021-09-02 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116080247/https://www.ecb.bt/rnp/election.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他們本來不打算就職<ref name="reuters">{{cite news |url=http://in.reuters.com/article/topNews/idINIndia-32738320080328 |title=Bhutan loses opposition as MPs cry foul over poll |work=Reuters India |date=2008-03-28 |accessdate=2008-12-11 |last=Denyer |first=Simon |archive-date=2008-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705230434/http://in.reuters.com/article/topNews/idINIndia-32738320080328 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是最後仍然以反對派議員的身份參加[[不丹國民議會|國會]]<ref>{{cite news|title=PDP to work towards a strong opposition|url=http://www.bbs.com.bt/PDP%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20strong%20opposition.html|accessdate=2013-03-29|newspaper=[[不丹广播公司|Bhutan Broadcasting Service]]|date=2008-04-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105011729/http://www.bbs.com.bt/PDP%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20strong%20opposition.html|archivedate=2014-01-05}}</ref>。國民議會首次會議在2008年4月21日召開，托傑擔任反對黨領袖<ref>{{cite news|title=Oath or Affirmation of Office|accessdate=2013-07-17|newspaper=Kuensel|date=2008-04-23}}</ref>。

他在2009年3月接任人民民主黨主席<ref>{{cite journal|title=Tshering Tobgay elected as the new PDP President|journal=The Week in Review|volume=3|issue=3|url=http://www.idsa.in/TWIR/3_3_2009_Bhutan|accessdate=2013-07-17|date=2009年3月|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091435/http://www.idsa.in/TWIR/3_3_2009_Bhutan|dead-url=no}}</ref>，復於2012年5月連任<ref>{{cite news|title=OL is the PDP President|url=http://www.bbs.bt/news/?p=12896|accessdate=2013-07-17|newspaper=Bhutan Broadcasting Service|date=2012-05-19|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804090935/http://www.bbs.bt/news/?p=12896|dead-url=no}}</ref>。並在2013年7月率領人民民主黨在[[2013年不丹國民議會選舉|國民議會選舉]]中取得32個議席（議席數目與上屆相同，超過全部議席數目的三分之二），上台執政。2013年7月29日，新一屆國民議會召開會議，托傑就任[[不丹首相|不丹首相]]<ref name=WashPost>{{cite news |title=Bhutan opposition party wins parliament election after calling for stronger ties with India |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/bhutan-opposition-party-wins-parliament-election-after-calling-for-stronger-ties-with-india/2013/07/14/d800c528-ec3b-11e2-818e-aa29e855f3ab_story.html |accessdate=2013-07-14 |newspaper=Washington Post |date=14 July 2013 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130716220449/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/bhutan-opposition-party-wins-parliament-election-after-calling-for-stronger-ties-with-india/2013/07/14/d800c528-ec3b-11e2-818e-aa29e855f3ab_story.html |archivedate=2013-07-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Lyonchhoen assumes office |url=http://www.bbs.bt/news/?p=29900 |accessdate=2021-09-02 |work=Bhutan Broadcasting Service |location=Thimphu |date=2013-07-29 |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815040658/http://www.bbs.bt/news/?p=29900 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他在2018年再次帶領人民民主黨參加[[2018年不丹國民議會選舉|國民議會選舉]]，卻在第一輪投票以第三位的成績落敗，全軍覆沒<ref>[https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/bhutan-pms-party-ousted-in-election/article24957312.ece Bhutan PM’s party ousted in election] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/bhutan-pms-party-ousted-in-election/article24957312.ece |date=20210902150608 }} The Hindu, 15 September 2018</ref>。

